    <div class="case-grid">
      <div class="info-card">
        <h4>The Business Problem</h4>
        <p>At Chase Bank, building business journeys (the workflows that define how tasks like customer onboarding run end to end) is a core activity for Servicing and OKYC product teams. The current process is heavily engineering-dependent. Product Managers spend significant time translating product requirements into technical specifications, creating repeated back-and-forth cycles, higher implementation risk and consistently long launch timelines.</p>
