      <div class="info-card">
        <h4>Research Objectives</h4>
        <p style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><strong>Design assumption under investigation:</strong> Empower Product Managers to build and test journeys independently via a no-code UI tool.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>What does the current journey configuration workflow actually look like?</li>
          <li>Which teams are involved at each stage, and what do they own?</li>
