        <p>A major Tier 1 UK bank had a commercial banking platform designed for finance teams managing money across large organisations, other banks, corporates, governments, schools and charities. The platform had not been redesigned in over twenty years. The bank needed to understand exactly what was breaking down in the experience before committing to a full redesign programme. The platform is role and task-centred, with the admin function sitting at the heart of every other interaction a customer's team has with the product.</p>
