    <div class="case-grid-3">
      <div class="insight-block gold-border"><h5>Critical Finding, The Admin Function</h5><p>The Admin section stood out as the most urgent pain point. Redundant user roles, overlong privilege lists and high dependency on bank support teams were causing real operational errors with genuine financial consequences for customers.</p></div>
      <div class="insight-block"><h5>Two Distinct Finance Team Mindsets</h5><p><strong>Large finance teams</strong> have clearly defined structures and need role-based access tied to specific responsibilities. <strong>Small finance teams</strong> carry overlapping responsibilities and need broader, more flexible privileges. Both were being served by the same one-size-fits-all admin flow.</p></div>
